1、please install node.js
2、cd in your project
3、install webpack :npm i webpack --save-dev
4、install webpack-dev-server:npm i webpack-dev-server --save
5、install ES2015:npm install --save-dev babel-preset-es2015 babel-preset-react
5、run ：npm install
6、run ：npm run build
7、run ：npm run dev
8、open your browser and input address ：http://localhost:8080/webpack-dev-server/